{"tid":1700422,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"玩快閃破壞既手足啲衣著可唔可以著得再公廁少少","createTime":"2019-11-08T13:57:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T16:50:23.000Z","uid":138026,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"519dc94d9b691fbf16f9cd9f5415f182e7526f36","tid":1700422,"uid":138026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T13:57:30.000Z","msg":"我係到提提各位想開破壞技既魔法師<br />\n除左著黑衫黑褲，帶帽，蒙面之外<br />\n你地對 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">鞋</span></span> 同個 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">背囊</span></span> 都好重要<br />\n請盡可能做到 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全黑</span></span><br />\n全黑唔得既話 都起碼用啲公廁款又或者用啲9成係黑色既袋同鞋<br />\n千祈唔好用啲一眼就影得岀既鞋同袋<br />\n有乜理由做啲危險野用啲咁容易認到既物品<br />\n<br />\n知我話緊你既 唔該你換左佢<br />\n唔好抱住僥倖既心態 宜啲野真係不可一不可再<br />\n我唔想見到你地因為對鞋同袋比人周到<br />\n我更加唔想遲啲係海邊見到岩先個幾對鞋<br />\n如果你地話冇錢買 我相信會有好多人幫你<br />\n唔好再咁傻豬啦好冇"},{"pid":"72a318b4272762172dd915998b0d897eeb97a2eb","tid":1700422,"uid":235477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T13:58:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6077e05b5ee56b165676958cb216ebefe5c81f65","tid":1700422,"uid":110207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T14:00:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">rain cover rain cover rain cover </span>"},{"pid":"3c113583012b92dbaadf7d41028979dde8059904","tid":1700422,"uid":138026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T14:03:27.000Z","msg":"我講緊你呀 同我換左佢呀<br />\n唔好再比我見到"},{"pid":"66b29876866bab0ee58540a9f92769b770a2922b","tid":1700422,"uid":103549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T14:04:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1bf57bb559aa18407db22405597bbfbbc53a32a5","tid":1700422,"uid":138026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T14:20:10.000Z","msg":"5年前 我仲係學生 我乜都做唔到<br />\n5年後  雖然我都仲係學生 但我有少少積蓄了<br />\n雖然我只係可以拎到千幾二千岀黎<br />\n但如果你地唔介意 我可以去h&amp;m平平地買對波鞋比你地換<br />\n對鞋著落未必會好舒服 但最少減低左比人周到既風險<br />\n求你地了"},{"pid":"eca415d305ec4d6f56bd1efe89e1448de5df05e1","tid":1700422,"uid":1646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T14:22:43.000Z","msg":"19蚊書包仲有冇？"},{"pid":"3879bbe660676ee03beda1f8ced89eb686a63fcb","tid":1700422,"uid":138026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eca415d305ec4d6f56bd1efe89e1448de5df05e1","tid":1700422,"uid":1646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T14:22:43.000Z","msg":"19蚊書包仲有冇？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T14:25:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"52b0fb459871a7e968c2e9b7589c4a7728262616","tid":1700422,"uid":138026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T14:33:59.000Z","msg":"係呀 我話緊你<br />\n學人開技又唔識隱藏身份<br />\n換左你對奇奇怪怪既鞋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ec4f9a69a772d7156bc5be07aeb5aaa72cb118b","tid":1700422,"uid":309045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T14:42:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a32aac23b7a449719eb13cf9243a1dc25f16b17","tid":1700422,"uid":138026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T14:44:16.000Z","msg":"推多12個鐘<br />\n等班傻豬魔法師知道佢地有幾引人注目之後我就唔推了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48fb588afa3d98e07d5c4cfba343db3324a32cda","tid":1700422,"uid":138026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T14:59:01.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd621f83f902115799711db1f5070d7417e48324","tid":1700422,"uid":263213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T15:00:39.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n鞋就痴膠紙啦至少都"},{"pid":"31a9c9da00ddb7146fe57253156d14e76f8213d5","tid":1700422,"uid":1219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T15:01:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/f